canonical view: 6795 records, 12450 tokens, 7384 source-form / 7152 ASCII types, but only 5242 best-available artifact clusters
CIEP: 5363 concordance rows -> 4203 CIE ids / 2130 known TM ids
single-word records: 4798/6795 (70.6%); translated singletons: 1795/2238 (80.2%)
exact duplicated multiword sequences: 25 groups / 51 records; cross-source 7, cross-artifact-proxy 12
